---
// Support component
---

<section id="support" class="support-section">
	<div class="support-container">
		<h2 class="support-title">支持我們</h2>

		<div class="support-content">
			<p class="support-paragraph">SITCON 秉持著不向與會者收費的原則，十年以來致力於推廣學生資訊教育，創造學生交流、教學互長的機會。</p>

			<p class="support-paragraph">
				如果您也認同 SITCON 的理念，歡迎以行動支持 SITCON 的運作，點擊下方「<a href="https://sitcon.org/donate" target="_blank">個人贊助方案</a>」，您的支持將會成為我們的動力，讓更多學生能在舞台上展現自我、讓資訊教育遍及臺灣的每個角落！
			</p>

			<p class="support-paragraph">
				若您有興趣成為我們的贊助夥伴，歡迎透過「<a href="https://sitcon.org/2026/cfs/" target="_blank">贊助徵求網頁</a>」，了解詳細合作方案，或是利用 <a
					href="mailto:contact@sitcon.org"
					target='_blank"'>contact@sitcon.org</a
				> 聯絡我們，我們將有專人與您商討更多的合作方式！
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="support-button-container">
			<a href="https://sitcon.org/donate" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="support-button" role="button" aria-label="個人贊助支持">個人贊助支持 ↗</a>
			<a href="https://sitcon.org/2026/cfs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="support-button" role="button" aria-label="前往 SITCON 2026 贊助徵求網頁">前往贊助徵求網頁 ↗</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.support-section {
		position: relative;
		margin: 0 auto;
		background-color: var(--white);
		color: #000;
		padding: 4rem 10rem;
		min-height: 70vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.support-container {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 0 40px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		max-width: 1200px;
	}

	.support-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		letter-spacing: 0.35rem;
	}

	.support-content {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	.support-button-container {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: end;
	}

	.support-button {
		background-color: #4285f4;
		color: var(--white);
		border: none;
		padding: 16px 32px;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.3);
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.support-button:hover {
		background-color: #3367d6;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.4);
	}

	.support-button:active {
		transform: translateY(0);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.3);
	}

	/* Responsive design */
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.support-section {
			padding: 2rem 0;
		}

		.support-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}

		.support-paragraph {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.support-button {
			padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}
	}
</style>
